                        <span class="visually-hidden">Loading...</span>
                    </div> School |
                    <div class="spinner-grow text-danger" role="status" style="margin-left:2%;margin-right:2%;">
                        <span class="visually-hidden">Loading...</span>
                    </div> College |
                    <div class="spinner-grow text-success" role="status" style="margin-left:2%;margin-right:2%;">
